="r-1692692719496" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1692692719496" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: block; flex-wrap: unset; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675767368623" data-id="1675767368623" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1692692719435" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1692692719435" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/gift-set" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/2ca47a71-3a7d-4345-9775-eb30911238d6/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/xmas-gift-bundles-tile.jpg" alt="Gift Sets & Bundles" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="864" height="540" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="864" natural-height="540" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1692692719393" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1692692719393"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><a href="/collections/gift-set" class="">Gift Sets & Bundles</a></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1692692719406" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1692692719406"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Gifts sets and bundles are great! When you're on the look-out for a present that gives just that little bit more, you can't beat them. A pen that comes with a bottle of ink? Excellent. One that's partnered with a matching notebook? Perfect. And what's more, they can have multiple uses. The contents of a bundle can be Secret Santa gifts, or stocking fillers, while sets can satisfy more than one. Gift the pen to one person, and the ink (or notebook) to another. Or keep one of them yourself! Nobody will know.</p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675767384572" data-id="1675767384572" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1692692719374" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1692692719374" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/quirky-gifts" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/8cb7a682-2f5c-4fe6-928b-c2723c0f1b89/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/fwp-quirky-hero.jpg" alt="Quirky Gifts" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="864" height="540" natural-width="864" natural-height="540" style="" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1692692719430" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1692692719430"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="background-color: rgba(51, 143, 255, 0.004);"><a href="/collections/quirky-gifts" class="">Quirky Gifts</a></span></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1692692719401" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1692692719401"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>We all know someone who’s not quite normal. Maybe some of us are not quite normal ourselves. A bit quirky. That’s ok, we don’t think that’s a bad thing. Normal is overrated. So we’ve picked out a few oddities for oddballs. Peculiarities for the peculiar ones. knick-knacks for nincompoops? Maybe not that one. But if you look through the list below and find yourself thinking “Oh, I know someone who likes that sort of stuff”, well, these are for them.</p><p></p></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1725524925878" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1725524925878"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1725524925787" data-id="1725524925787"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1682421716748" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1682421716748"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Christmas Bestsellers</h3></div></div><div data-label="Carousel" data-key="carousel" data-atomgroup="module" id="m-1679585158321" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-carousel" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1679585158321"><div class="module main-slider owl-carousel owl-theme " data-collg="3" data-colmd="3" data-colsm="3" data-colxs="1" data-marginlg="5px" data-marginmd="5px" data-marginsm="5px" data-marginxs="5px" data-dotslg="0" data-dotsmd="0" data-dotssm="0" data-dotsxs="0" data-navlg="1" data-navmd="1" data-navsm="1" data-navxs="1" data-navspeed="1200" data-autoplay="1" data-autoplaytimeout="5000" data-au